data.description: This is a beautiful home and a must see!  Walk into large living room perfect for entertaining. Updated kitchen with granite counter tops.  Step outside in the rear to a private, spacious, fenced in yard  great for a garden and  pets. Newer roof and furnace.  Finished game room in the lower level with updated full bath.  Primary bedroom has two closets and a deck off from the bedroom.  Make this house your new home.
